name: TRIUMPH OF DEATH - Wrath of the Dead
description:
"On the eve of the Apocalypse, the Four Horsemen betray their Horses.
They slit their throats and assemble their jawbones into a device large enough to plow up the waiting world.
They plowed the fields and scattered their dead horses over the land.
The Air is choked with horsehair and Hell is paved with Horseflesh."

JPEG, 200 DPI 11000 x 4856 px PPP (Progressive Photon Prepassrendering)
